{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_13_level_main_13-01_beg","storyGroup":"main_13","storySort":144,"storyDependence":"main_13_level_main_13-01_beg","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"13-2","storyName":"眼前的伤","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"整合运动在收拢伦蒂尼姆附近的感染者，营地却被一群维多利亚残兵攻击，Guard辨识出他们其实已经感染。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_13-01_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_13-01","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":0,"next":2,"characters":["？？？","珀茜瓦尔","Guard","萨卡兹流浪者","愤恨的士官","雷德","九","受伤的士兵"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"charslot","id":4},{"type":"background","id":5},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$mist_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_mist_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_43_i01.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"5","block":"true","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":11},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":12},{"type":"sticker","id":13,"multi":"true","text":"好热。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":14,"multi":"true","text":"\\n太阳在燃烧，我在燃烧。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":15},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":16},{"type":"dialog","id":17},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walk_water","volume":"0.5","id":18},{"type":"imagetween","image":"43_i01","screenadapt":"coverall","xScaleFrom":"1","yScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"1.2","yScaleTo":"1.2","yTo":"20","block":"false","duration":"40","id":19},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":20},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":21},{"type":"sticker","id":22,"multi":"true","text":"那里是出口吗？","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":23,"multi":"true","text":"\\n还差一点，只有几步了。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":24,"multi":"true","text":"\\n我只要迈开腿就行，也许这些火，这些愤怒，这些痛苦和悔恨都是幻觉。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":25},{"type":"sticker","id":26,"multi":"true","text":"......","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":27,"multi":"true","text":"\\n也许出路才是幻觉，我不知道。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":28},{"type":"sticker","id":29,"multi":"true","text":"可他们还在我的背后看着，那些目光......他们在审视我吗？还是仅仅是，看着我，看着我会如何背负他们的死亡。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":30,"multi":"true","text":"\\n他们的每项事迹都如此光辉，他们都是最了不起的人。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":31},{"type":"sticker","id":32,"multi":"true","text":"我的队长，还有那位传奇的萨卡兹斥候，以及......大尉，最后的纯血温迪戈。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":33,"multi":"true","text":"\\n他们都死了，在我的面前，在我的身后。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":34,"multi":"true","text":"\\n如此不值一提的我却活了下来，他们让我活了下来。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":35,"multi":"true","text":"\\n他们究竟，对我怀有怎样的期待？","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":36},{"type":"sticker","id":37,"multi":"true","text":"我没法儿去想......我没法儿不去想。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":38,"multi":"true","text":"\\n我不能辜负这些死亡，我绝不能辜负。他们的死必须要有意义。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":39},{"type":"sticker","id":40,"multi":"true","text":"哪怕烈日灼身，我必须迎向太阳。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":41,"multi":"true","text":"\\n直到被焚烧殆尽，直到——我终于可以无愧地面对他们。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":42},{"type":"dialog","id":43},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"4","id":44},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":45},{"type":"image","id":46},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":47},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_bg_34_g10_tent_inside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":48},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":49},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":50},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":51,"musicid":1},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"唔......","id":52},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"我说，你每次都能在换岗前这么刚巧地醒过来？","id":54,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"这是你以前刻苦训练的成果吗，Guard？","id":56,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":57},{"type":"charslot","id":58},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":59},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#2$1","focus":"m","duration":"1","id":60},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"......珀茜瓦尔。","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":63},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":64},{"type":"sticker","id":65,"multi":"true","text":"我尽量伸展了下身体，睡得不算好，除了一场接着一场的噩梦，我腿上的伤也还在隐隐作痛。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":66,"multi":"true","text":"\\n为了追上九的队伍，我们差点一头撞进了维多利亚军队的阵线里。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":67},{"type":"sticker","id":68,"multi":"true","text":"我负责接头的那批感染者，他们平常在镇子里被人吐唾沫，觉着生活已经没有了任何希望，可他们从没走进过真正的战场。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":69,"multi":"true","text":"\\n他们差点被吓傻了。我其实好些......但我痛恨我的适应。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":70,"multi":"true","text":"\\n我们能顺利抵达驻地简直花光了我这辈子所有的好运气。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":71},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":72},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"只是太热了，到了晚上还是这么闷。","id":74,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"还有多长时间换岗？","id":76,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"十五分钟吧，你可以再坐一会儿。","id":78,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"我去洗把脸。","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":81},{"type":"charslot","id":82},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":83},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":84},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"你的腿怎么了，怎么一瘸一拐的？","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"......结晶蔓延过去了？","id":88,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"还不是今天。","id":90,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"帮我递下毛巾，珀茜瓦尔，你左手边。","id":92,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"粉色碎花的这条？","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"......呃，对。","id":96,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":97},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":98},{"type":"sticker","id":99,"multi":"true","text":"我看到珀茜瓦尔挑了挑眉毛。我很想和她解释，半岛郡那家纺织厂老板送给我们的毛巾都是这个样式，雷德也有条差不多的。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":100,"multi":"true","text":"\\n那老板是个满脸褶子的男人，他运气不错，结晶长在肚子上，用衣服一遮就看不出来。但愿他现在还没被人发现。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":101},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":102},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"算了。","id":104,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"你带回来的人比我们一开始预计的多，看来就算没直接成为战场，周边那些小城镇的状况也在恶化。","id":106,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"影响的范围比想象中大太多了。那些领地上的贵族......呵。他们当然视而不见。","id":108,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"那些镇子原本就是靠着和商队做生意生存，现在打仗了，没有运输队去伦蒂尼姆，他们还能有什么好日子过。","id":110,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"日子坏起来，感染者最先倒霉。以前他们还能在镇子的最边缘偷偷种点粮食。村里人也会和他们做点小买卖，毕竟，赚谁的钱都是赚。","id":112,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"只是，以前生活还算松快，大家还在乎体面，现在呢......","id":114,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"到了算账的时候了。","id":116,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"珀茜瓦尔，眼下快到豆子成熟的季节了，田里那些他们忙了一季的苗已经开始结豆荚了......他们却选择现在加入我们，逃开。","id":118,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"这些感染者扔下了已经浇灌了那么久的土地，放弃了几个月后，乃至未来永远的收成，也要离开这里。","id":120,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"他们......一定是真的没有一点办法了。","id":122,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"我们，感染者们，也许早就对这种“剥夺”习以为常。","id":124,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"但这不能是每次的结论。","id":126,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":127},{"type":"charslot","id":128},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"先生，您还在休息吗？","id":130},{"type":"dialog","id":131},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","duration":"1","id":132},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"先生，我听到说话声，您果然醒了。","id":134,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"又是你，我都说了——","id":136,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"您这是要去值夜班吗？","id":138,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"要来点夜宵吗？我这里有罐头，维多利亚产的。口味不算好，但很方便！","id":140,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"香烟？酒？说不定能帮您在夜里提提神，都很干净！还有磨刀石，施术单元，什么都有！","id":142,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"珀茜瓦尔小姐，要不要点毛发护理膏？现在这东西可不好找，毕竟会随身带这种东西的都是军官。","id":144,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"而军官比较难死？","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"也不是，只是把他们从死人堆里挖出来比较难，他们一般都压在最下面。","id":148,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"......你又想要换我们的药？","id":150,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"这个，我，我总感觉最近很不舒服，身上疼得厉害，还有些幻觉......我很怕石头在往我脑子里长。","id":152,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"你每天往那些飘满了粉尘的弹坑里钻，矿石病不恶化才怪。","id":154,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"我们能折腾出来的只是最最基础的粗制药，能多少抑制点病情的发展而已，别以为吃了那东西能保命。","id":156,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"我知道，我知道，我——","id":158,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"我知道你在倒卖我们的药。","id":160,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"我接来的这批感染者告诉我，他们从一个骑摩托的萨卡兹那里买过些抗矿石病的药，“效果不错”。","id":162,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"这个，可是——","id":164,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"赚得不少吧？就按照你口袋里硬币的数量来决定你的惩罚如何？","id":166,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f9/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"......","id":168,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"我只是，呃，让合适的东西出现在需要的地方，毕竟......这里在打仗。","id":170,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"我们不会警告你第二次。","id":172,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"......但至少你给他们了。我们确实没有信使给所有人发药。","id":174,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"我保证！今后不会了，这次我只要一点！几片都行！我......我这几天都在发烧。","id":176,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"Guard？","id":178,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"......","id":180,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"帮他申请点药吧，这次把他登记下来。","id":182,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"谢谢，谢谢你们！","id":184,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"别谢我们，去谢谢医生们。","id":186,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"他们在实验室不小心得了矿石病，公司不愿意再付保险钱。从一个前途无量的精英，变成一个该死的感染者，接受这种转变并不容易。","id":188,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"还好他们听说过整合运动，他们找上了我们。","id":190,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"不应该也谢谢你的老东家吗？","id":192,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"我对他们不止有感谢。但他们也永远不会原谅我......我自己选的。","id":194,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"不过罗德岛的设备精度太高了，我们学不来。算了，我们毕竟不是真的在开发药物。","id":196,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"......是啊，我们吃药不是为了治好自己，只是为了，暂时先活下去。","id":198,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"打针和吃药解决不了矿石病。","id":200,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":201},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":202},{"type":"sticker","id":203,"multi":"true","text":"我至今都记得，还在罗德岛的时候，经常能看到医疗部里来去匆匆的研究员们，还有凯尔希医生在实验室里的背影。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":204,"multi":"true","text":"\\n如果这片大地上有一个机构，它的身上有着彻底医治矿石病的希望，那一定是罗德岛。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":205,"multi":"true","text":"\\n我选择了背叛。我知道，我没有资格，但我......偶尔......仍为曾经是其中的一员自豪。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":206},{"type":"sticker","id":207,"multi":"true","text":"但——真正治愈矿石病的那天什么时候才会到来？","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":208,"multi":"true","text":"\\n五十年，一百年，还是下一个千年？在这种药被研究出来之前，感染者又该怎么办？","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":209,"multi":"true","text":"\\n矿石病早已不再只是一种疾病。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":210},{"type":"sticker","id":211,"multi":"true","text":"它是别人仇恨的视线，是理所当然的欺辱，是方便的归罪，是下意识的指责。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":212,"multi":"true","text":"\\n在这里的每个人都经历过类似的故事。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":213,"multi":"true","text":"\\n这些事......怎么能靠药物解决？","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":214,"multi":"true","text":"\\n就好像逆水行舟，这片大地不是光明的道德天国。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":215},{"type":"sticker","id":216,"multi":"true","text":"所以，我们才不能放下可耻而伟大的暴力。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":217,"multi":"true","text":"\\n......但也许......不。那是很久以后的事。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":218},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":219},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"对了，你叫什么名字？","id":221,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"我？呃......","id":223,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"这个嘛......“卖药佣兵”？“骑摩托车的”？我还没混到需要别人记住我的那个地步。","id":225,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"这可算不上名字。","id":227,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/35/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"我想想，我得想个威风的——","id":229,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":230},{"type":"charslot","id":231},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":232},{"type":"playsound","key":"$firemagic_explosion","volume":"0.4","id":233},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1.5","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":234},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":235},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹流浪者","text":"怎、怎么了？","id":237,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":238},{"type":"charslot","id":239},{"type":"playsound","key":"$swordtsing4","volume":"0.4","id":240},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":241},{"type":"playsound","key":"$swordtsing5","volume":"0.4","id":242},{"type":"delay","time":"0.3","id":243},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":244},{"type":"sticker","id":245,"multi":"true","text":"喊叫声，还有刀剑的碰撞声。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":246},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":247},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"萨卡兹，去后面避难。","id":249,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d8/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"珀茜瓦尔，安抚下那些刚加入我们的平民，他们暂时经不起惊吓。","id":251,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":252},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":253},{"type":"sticker","id":254,"multi":"true","text":"我的手抚向身后的武器，这把剑永远准备万全。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":255},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":256},{"type":"dialog","id":257},{"type":"charslot","duration":"2","id":258},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":259},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":260},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":261},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/cc/Avg_bg_34_g9_tent.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":262},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":263},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":264},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$plot_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_plot_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":265,"musicid":2},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"嗬——嗬——","id":267,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_334","focus":"m","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雷德","text":"你一定要我杀了你？你的队伍看起来状态可并不好。","id":269,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_334.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":270},{"type":"charslot","id":271},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":272},{"type":"sticker","id":273,"multi":"true","text":"一群满身淤青和尘土的维多利亚军人被我们的战士团团围住。领头的士官喘着粗气，身上还留着新鲜的伤痕。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":274,"multi":"true","text":"\\n这......真的是一场袭击？","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":275},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":276},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"九，怎么回事？","id":278,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d8/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"这帮人从北边摸进了林子，罗曼内奇中了一箭，医生正在处理。","id":280,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"就这二十一个人，还有三五个躺在担架上，他们居然想袭击我们的营地？疯了。","id":282,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"哈！瞧瞧啊，在我们国家的腹地，伟大首都的周边，我看到了什么？","id":284,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"一大群该死的整合运动感染者！杀了我！来，有本事杀了我！要不然就让我杀了你们！","id":286,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"阴谋家，煽动者，暴徒，杀人犯......脓疮、脓疮、脓疮！","id":288,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"怪不得我们打得那么艰难，光凭那些野蛮的魔族佬怎么可能战胜我们？真正的敌人来自我们身边，来自我们背后！","id":290,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"哪里有混乱，哪里就有你们的影子，哪里就有感染者的影子！","id":292,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"看来你们刚从前线撤下来。","id":294,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"你们士气低落，编制不全，伤口包扎得很潦草......看装备型号，你们不是职业军人。征召兵？","id":296,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_423_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的士兵","text":"我们是法夫公爵第四步兵营......几连来着？所属黑溪村小队和东汉姆村小队，你们这里有医生吗？","id":298,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_avg_npc_423_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":299},{"type":"charslot","id":300},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"r","id":301},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_423_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":302},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"闭嘴，士兵！举好你的武器！","id":304,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_423_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的士兵","text":"可是，上士，维克多他......","id":306,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_avg_npc_423_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"r","id":307},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"我命令你，举好武器！","id":309,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":310},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"别这么大吼大叫的，维多利亚人。后面的营地还有平民在休息。","id":312,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"你们维多利亚的平民。","id":314,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"平民？如果他们不加入你们，他们不选择成为暴徒和帮凶，维多利亚自会给他们应有的生活！","id":316,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"我问你，为什么那些龌龊的人通通都是感染者？","id":318,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"为什么我的国家里，贫民区的流氓，荒地上的劫匪，邪恶暴虐的魔族，还有你们，满怀阴谋的整合运动，你们都是感染者？","id":320,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"为什么我们可敬的法夫公爵没有感染，为什么伟大的弗雷德里克三世陛下没有感染，为什么正直与道德的人就不会被矿石病侵袭？","id":322,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"人们到底是因感染而卑劣......还是因为卑劣而感染？","id":324,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"那你呢？","id":326,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"难道是卑劣传染了吗？","id":328,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"你胆敢——","id":330,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":331},{"type":"charslot","id":332},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_423_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":333},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_241#1","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"20,0","focus":"l","id":334},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的士兵","text":"够了！","id":336,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_avg_npc_423_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":337},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"100,0","duration":"0.3","block":"true","id":338},{"type":"delay","time":"0.1","id":339},{"type":"playsound","key":"$fightgeneral","text":"","id":340},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":341},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"5","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":342},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","posfrom":"100,0","posto":"50,0","duration":"1","block":"true","id":343},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","posfrom":"20,0","posto":"240,0","duration":"1","id":344},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":345},{"type":"dialog","id":346},{"type":"charslot","id":347},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":348},{"type":"sticker","id":349,"multi":"true","text":"这个维多利亚的士官瞪大了眼睛，下意识地侧过身子，想把自己的胳膊藏在我的视线之外。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":350,"multi":"true","text":"\\n他的嘴唇翕动了几下，却什么都没有说出来。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":351},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":352},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_423_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":353},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的士兵","text":"我们现在也都是......龌龊的人，卑劣的人！","id":355,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_avg_npc_423_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_423_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":356},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的士兵","text":"......难道不是吗，长官？","id":357,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_avg_npc_423_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"我......","id":359,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"这不一样，这是光荣的......","id":361,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"你的手臂。","id":363,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":364},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"我看得到，那些刚刚冒头的结晶。你的病情发展得很快。","id":365,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"......我在为我的国家拼杀！我在杀那些萨卡兹，只是不小心沾上了点砂石，也可能是魔族的血——","id":367,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":368},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"......","id":369,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":370},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"你们应征入伍的时候学了什么？没有一点有关活性源石环境的警告吗？","id":371,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_423_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":372},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的士兵","text":"教官告诉我们，学会扣扳机射弩箭就行了......我们就学了两个星期。","id":373,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_avg_npc_423_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":374},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"想必也没有配发任何阻断剂。","id":375,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_423_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":376},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的士兵","text":"呃......什么阻断剂？","id":377,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_avg_npc_423_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":378},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"......我估计他们所有人都感染了，九。","id":379,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_423_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的士兵","text":"怎、怎么可能？我一周前才在连队里做的体检，很健康！","id":381,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_avg_npc_423_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"一周......感染很迅速。又或者，他们只是为了让你们继续待在前线，撒了谎？","id":383,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"住口！","id":385,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"那几个躺在担架上的，已经昏迷多久了？他们很危险。","id":387,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_423_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":388},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的士兵","text":"什、什么？","id":389,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_avg_npc_423_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":390},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"急性发作导致的死亡和崩解，对你们，对我们，都很危险。","id":391,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":392},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"你们一直抬着担架赶路，让昏迷的伤员仰面向上是个正确的选择，这样能防止他们在无意识的状况下窒息。","id":393,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","focus":"m","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"可是......你们检查过他们的背后吗？","id":395,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"......","id":397,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":398},{"type":"charslot","id":399},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":400},{"type":"sticker","id":401,"multi":"true","text":"突然沉默下来的士官缓步走到了担架之前，犹豫着想为躺在上面的人翻个身，伸出的手却在碰到他身体的一瞬间缩了回来。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":402,"multi":"true","text":"\\n士官手足无措，简直像是在面对一个会放电会喷毒，还会随时跳起来咬人一口的致命牙兽。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":403,"multi":"true","text":"\\n那可是他的战友。在成为战友之前，他们也许是......我不知道，耕种同一片土地的表兄弟？","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":404},{"type":"sticker","id":405,"multi":"true","text":"我叹了口气，扶起了担架上昏迷的维多利亚士兵。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":406,"multi":"true","text":"\\n我们不用为他脱下外套检查了，源石结晶已经刺破了他背后的衣服。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":407},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":408},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":409},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"这......","id":410,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_423_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":411},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的士兵","text":"维克多！该死！","id":412,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_avg_npc_423_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_423_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的士兵","text":"我不该拉他来前线的......他爸要是知道他感染了，会杀了他，再杀了我！","id":414,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_avg_npc_423_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":415},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"那些萨卡兹，他们的巫术把我们变成了感染者！我早就听说过，魔族的诅咒！","id":416,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":417},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"他们玷污了我们的土地，还要污染我们的道德！","id":418,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":419},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"闭上嘴吧。","id":420,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":421},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"萨卡兹天生易感，他们的军队里几乎都是感染者。你们杀死他们，或者得了病的你们被他们杀死......","id":422,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":423},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"如果没人处理尸体，就会......","id":424,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":425},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":426},{"type":"sticker","id":427,"multi":"true","text":"我没有往下说。我听见了某个声音。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":428,"multi":"true","text":"\\n这种声音我很熟悉。不论在雷姆必拓，还是在罗德岛，还是现在。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":429,"multi":"true","text":"\\n这是每个感染者最恐惧的声音。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":430,"multi":"true","text":"\\n我们自己破碎的声音。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":431},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":432},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_423_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的士兵","text":"......我感觉我在战壕里听过......某些声音......","id":434,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_avg_npc_423_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_423_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":435},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的士兵","text":"上士，您那时告诉我，那是炮声！","id":436,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_avg_npc_423_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":437},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"那就是炮声！","id":438,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":439},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"我们的敌人试图用一切手段伤害我们和我们的国家，包括他们的死亡！","id":440,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"魔族佬，流寇，塔拉人......在弗雷德里克三世陛下还在的时候，从来没有这些破事！","id":442,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":443},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"我们......我们必须将这些渣滓驱逐出维多利亚，我们......","id":444,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":445},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"我们......","id":446,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_241#1","focus":"m","id":447},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤恨的士官","text":"我们能做什么......？我们能救维克多的命吗？我们......我们在光荣的维多利亚的庇护下......","id":448,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":449},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"......","id":450,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":451},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"白痴。","id":452,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":453},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"我再说一遍，你是个感染者了，病入膏肓。","id":454,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":455},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"我可以说得再明确一点，和我们一样，和在这里的所有人一样......","id":456,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1065_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":457},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Guard","text":"你就快要死了。","id":458,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_1065_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":459},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":460},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":461},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":462},{"type":"character","id":463},{"type":"image","id":464}],"characters":["？？？","珀茜瓦尔","Guard","萨卡兹流浪者","愤恨的士官","雷德","九","受伤的士兵"]}